	(lib_symbols)
	(text "CHORUS TIMEBASE HAT - REV A\n\nArchitecture Overview:\n- Single 24.576 MHz TCXO master clock\n- STM32C011F4P6 timebase MCU (Cortex-M0+)\n- PCM5122 stereo DAC with external MCLK\n- Raspberry Pi 5 HAT form factor\n\nSheet Index:\n1. Power Supply (3.3V Digital, 3.3V Analog)\n2. TCXO & Clock Distribution\n3. STM32 Timebase MCU\n4. PCM5122 Audio DAC\n5. Connectors & Debug\n5. Schmidt Triggers\n"
